description: [``botocore``] Private Certificate Authority service now supports P521 and RSA3072 key algorithms.
[``botocore``] Introduced support for Skew Protection. Added enableSkewProtection field to createBranch and updateBranch API.
[``botocore``] AWS CodeBuild now supports webhook filtering by organization name
[``botocore``] This release adds support to update projects and environments
[``botocore``] Generate account endpoints for DynamoDB requests using ARN-sourced account ID when available

[``botocore``] This release changes the CreateLaunchTemplate, CreateLaunchTemplateVersion, ModifyLaunchTemplate CLI and SDKs such that if you do not specify a client token, a randomly generated token is used for the request to ensure idempotency.
[``botocore``] IVS Real-Time now offers customers the ability to adjust the participant & composition recording segment duration
[``botocore``] Updated CreateLogAnomalyDetector to accept only kms key arn

[``botocore``] This release adds the ResetChannelState and ResetOriginEndpointState operation to reset MediaPackage V2 channel and origin endpoint. This release also adds a new field, UrlEncodeChildManifest, for HLS/LL-HLS to allow URL-encoding child manifest query string based on the requirements of AWS SigV4.
[``botocore``] Updating GetDataAccess response for S3 Access Grants to include the matched Grantee for the requested prefix
